initial_question.body:
Tried this plugin yesterday, works on android but on iOS ( 15+ ) device tested it ever only returns an identityToken. Repeated the stop using Apple ID and login cycle like 20 times, whilst using the old cordova-plugin-sign-in-with-apple retuns the user data on the initial login:

```
        await SocialLogin.initialize({
          apple: {
            clientId,
          },
        });

        const { result } = (await SocialLogin.login({
          provider: "apple",
          options: {
            scopes: ["email", "profile"],
          },
        })) as { result: AppleProviderResponse };
```
